{
  "stem": "740.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, of course, as I understood later, in those days already the Nazi movement was strong.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You could hear the SR marching through the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I looked as golden blond with blue eyes, like a little German boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Nobody took me for a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I took advantage of it, inadvertently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When I was six years old, I started my first day in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, again, according to the wishes of my mother, it was, was called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is a free school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You don't learn ABC.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You learn citizenship.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was really, I think, promoted and sponsored by the communistic movement in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That's what it really was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Matter of fact, in the [GERMAN], one of those streets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We lived in the northern part, which is about-- anybody who knows Berlin, it's about five blocks away from Alexanderplatz, that close to the business center of the city.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was called [GERMAN], N-54, North 54.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "My first year in school was terrific.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The teacher loved me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He loved my mother, apparently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I had a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Unfortunately, about a month before going into the second grade, my mother had a nicotine poisoning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Apparently she hacked while she had asthma, and a little tiny opening in the lungs created the poisoning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They put her in a hospital, of course [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they closed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Apparently, somehow it correlated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Two days later, she had a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Another day later, she had pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And now comes the interesting part, because in many respects, Hitler was shortly before the rise.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "This is 1933, now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And, of course, a little guy still does know him from Adam.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And the father doesn't tell him anything because, you know, he's too young.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
